    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car is in truly pristine, showroom-level condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it from day one! It looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot, with not a single blemish to be found. If you're looking for perfection, this is definitely the one. I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate a ride this flawless!",
