    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously garaged and climate-controlled since day one. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, completely free of any swirls, rock chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin still carries that distinctive new-car scent; the premium leather seats are supple, showing zero signs of bolster wear or creasing. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the adaptive cruise control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented exclusively at authorized dealerships. The engine bay is immaculate, and the high-performance tires have less than 1,000 miles of wear. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the discerning driver who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
